{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2012}} {{Infobox ethnic group |group = Pakistanis in Iran |image = |caption = |population = 11,000<ref>[[:File:Pakistani Diaspora.svg]] Retrieved 29 April 2013.</ref> |popplace = [[Tehran]], [[Mashhad]] |langs = [[Urdu]]{{·}} [[Saraiki language|Saraiki]] {{·}} [[Punjabi language|Punjabi]]{{·}} [[Balochi language|Balochi]]{{·}} [[Persian language|Persian]] |rels = [[Islam]] }}
'''Pakistanis in Iran''' consist of expatriates from [[Pakistan]] living in [[Iran]], as well as locally born people with ancestral roots in Pakistan. According to the ''[[Overseas Pakistanis Foundation]]'', their population is estimated at 11,000 in 2004-2005.<ref> and also those who study in various Islamic universities in Qom and Mashad [http://www.opf.org.pk/download/anual/YEARBK.pdf Overseas Pakistanis Foundation 2004-2005 Yearbook pg 31] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100524170403/http://www.opf.org.pk/download/anual/YEARBK.pdf |date=24 May 2010 }} Retrieved 7 September 2010.</ref> While many tend to be students, there are a number of white-collar professionals employed in various jobs. The majority of the population is centred on [[Tehran]][[Mashhad]]. Dr. Muhammad Irfan-Maqsood is a well known Pakistani entrepreneur active in Iran and well known for his program ScienceTech+ and KarafarinShow. He has been awarded four time top Iranian National Sheikhbahai Entrepreneurship Award from 2013-2016.<ref>[https://news.um.ac.ir/news-13440.html Ferdowsi University of Mashhad News Page] Published 22 Khordad 1396.</ref><ref>[http://tn.ai/1523654 Tasnim News Agency 2017] Published 7 September 2010.</ref><ref>[http://www.kstp.ir/Portal/Home/Post/%D8%A8%D8%B1%DA%AF%D8%B2%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C-%DA%AF%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%87%D9%85%D8%A7%DB%8C%DB%8C-%DA%A9%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A2%D9%81%D8%B1%DB%8C%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A8%DB%8C%D9%86%E2%80%8C%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%84%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%B3%D8%A7%DB%8C%D9%86%D8%B3%E2%80%8C-%D8%AA%DA%A9%E2%80%8C%D9%BE%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B3-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D9%85%D8%B4%D9%87%D8%AF-2017 پارک علم و فناوری خراسان KSTP PR] Published 15 February 2017.</ref><ref>[http://www.sciencetechplus.com ScienceTech+ Homepage] Published 15 January 2017.</ref><ref>[http://www.karafarinshow.com KarafarinShow 2017 Homepage] Published 10 October 2017.</ref>He also has been awarded as the Young Entrepreneur of Iran by Ministry of Sports and Youth Affairs, Iran in 2018.<ref>[http