==== Verbs ==== # Non finite forms ## Infinitive: stem + an (''karan -'' 'to do/make') # Tense-aspect forms ## Imperative Singular: stem, Imperative Plural: stem + V ## Present-future: root + endings - 1st: - m, 2nd: -s, 3rd: -e, 1st plural: -en ## Definite Present: da/de + present-future
==== Example Sentences ==== * ''Abo-e kata dur thi?'' ('Village' + 'how much far' + 'is') ** "How far is your village?" * ''Pali de kham'' ('Bread' + Definite Future + 'Eat') ** "I am eating bread." * ''La brok odasta ga'' ('He' + 'Very' + 'Hungry' + 'become/go') ** "He became very hungry" * ''Ao mara ga-m'' ('I' + 'die' + 'become') ** "I died/am dead"
